{
  "chapter": 115,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙在练武场训练小盘和小贲剑术，教导他们实战无规矩的道理，小贲展现出忠诚护主之心。朱姬出现邀项少龙闲聊，透露秦廷内高陵君和阳泉君两大势力觊觎王位的政治格局，并对项少龙流露出暧昧情感，项少龙谨慎应对后告辞。乌府召开出使前会议，乌应元、滕翼、陶方等商讨留守和物资安排，项少龙拒绝以歌姬作礼。次日项少龙继续训练两小子，琴清出现与他交谈，对他不慕权势的态度产生好奇和好感，提及\"一滴蜜糖\"寓言后含羞离去。项少龙深感情感之累，渴望完成使命后退隐。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "小贲是气我不守规矩，竟出脚来踢你？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "speaker_name": "小王贲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小贲不敢！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "假若你现在是对阵沙场，能怪敌人拿脚来踢你吗？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "speaker_name": "小王贲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小贲受教了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "那还不给我滚起来动手！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "小贲想以血肉之躯来挡利剑吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "speaker_name": "小王贲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "爹曾教小贲，宁死也要护着太子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "若你刚才剑没脱手，便可用剑来挡格，是吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "speaker_name": "小贲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太傅真厉害，爹从不懂得在比剑时踢我。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎可如此比较，来！让我先教你们捱打的功夫。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！那最好……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项太傅有空和我闲聊两句吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "姬后有此懿旨，少龙怎敢不从？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "见你不到几天，你又要走了，真教人惆怅。唉！我该怎么感激你才行哩？你不但救了我两母子，又为人家向乐乘和赵穆讨回公道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "是少龙的分内事嘛！姬后有命，完成不了的话，是鄙人的失职。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你也来和我耍这一套，现在人人对我又敬又怕，若连你这知己也是诚惶诚恐，教我向谁倾吐心事，不韦已对我如避蛇蝎，你也要学他那样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "天下最可怕的地方，莫过于宫廷，姬后难道不晓得有人日思夜梦都想取你们母子之位而代之吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "说到玩手段，我朱姬怕过谁来，项太傅放心。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要时常摆起一副防人家引诱你的戒备模样好吗？宫廷的生活有时虽闷了点儿，但只要看着政儿日渐成长，我已感到满足快乐，其他一切并不介意。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "现在究竟有哪些人在觊觎王位呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在秦廷内没有多少人对我两母子看得顺眼，主要是以高陵君和阳泉君为首的两批人，其他不是给不韦收买就是观风之辈，我不信他们能有多大作为。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "谁是高陵君？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "高陵君就是嬴傒，大王的宝座本应是属于他的，却因华阳夫人的干预，改立大王，嬴傒虽获封高陵，但受奸鬼杜仓的影响，一直含恨在心，四处散播不韦和大王合谋害死先王的谣言，意图不轨，说到底不过是想自己当秦君罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "至于阳泉君则与秀丽夫人秘密勾结，又得到军方部分不知死活的将领支持，希冀能改立成蟜做太子。幸好两党人各有所图，阳泉君和高陵君又一向不和，势若水火，否则大王和不韦更头痛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要谈这些令人心烦的事好吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "我不过在关心姬后罢了！究竟大将军是否支持阳泉君呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你说王龁吗？他只忠于大王，又看不起阳泉君，除非有人能拿出证据证明小政不是大王的骨肉，否则大将军绝不会站在阳泉君的一方。嘻！这事有什么方法证实哩！难道他们敢逼大王滴血认亲吗？即使要认我也不怕。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "难道你也认为政儿不是大王的骨肉吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "姬后误会！嘿！少龙还要回去打点行装。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你再诸多借口躲开人家，朱姬会恨死你哩！我又不是逼你私通，只不过说些心事话儿，有什么好怕的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "你不怕大王不高兴吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大王什么都好，又宠爱人家，唉！我不想再说了。少龙！祝你一路顺风，好安然地回来见人家。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "未来一年，会是我们到咸阳后最艰苦的一段时间，不但少龙出使六国，吕相亦要东征周室，相国府只剩下图先坐镇，恐怕撑不住大局，幸好近年来我打通很多人事上的关系，只要低调一点，应可安然度过。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "刚才我们商量过，乌卓大哥和乌果留下照料府务，以防有起事来，不致全无抗手之力。且在这段时间里，大部分人均迁到牧场去，好避开咸阳城的风风雨雨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "不若二哥也留下吧！二嫂临盆在即，二……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事休要再提，此行表面虽看似凶险不大，但六国形势诡变难测，要我留在这里，怎可安寝睡觉？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不能随三弟出使，确是遗憾，又没有其他方法，唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你两位兄长为你在家将中挑出十二名武技高明的人做你的亲随，这批高手人人能以一挡十，可成你的好帮手。少龙千万不要落单，很多人恨不得能把你拔除。听说阳泉君会派出高手在途中刺杀你，一来可拔掉他们的眼中钉，又可打击吕相的威信，少龙千万要小心才好。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕相刚和我商量过出使的事宜，吕相会拨出一批珍宝和三千镒黄金，供你送礼之用。我们则精挑百匹良骥，一批歌姬，另外再加三千镒黄金，足可够少龙应付很多贪得无厌的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这足够我挥霍十世了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "送什么也没有问题，但小婿却怎也不惯以歌姬作礼物，岳丈大人可否收回此项？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙既有此古怪想法，我也不会勉强。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "唉！项太傅！政太子又耽误时间了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅早安，让我立即把太子唤来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "难得太子兴高采烈，项太傅又远行在即，让他缺一天课好了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅请坐！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太子像对太傅特别依恋，有你在之时他特别兴奋，平时却沉默得不像他那年纪的孩子，总像满怀心事似的，教人看得心痛。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "你刚才明明占上风，为何白白错过机会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "speaker_name": "小贲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小贲怕误伤太子，会杀头哩！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "什么？谁要你让我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_ben",
      "text": "哪叫你是太子哩！不过只要依着我的方法练习，绝不会轻易受伤。下回你们近身搏斗时，可在地上加铺数层厚席，那什么问题都没有。练习前须做足热身的动作，就更万无一失，清楚了吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 115,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "小孩子是最可爱的，不过只要想到有一天他会变成像我们一般，再不懂以单纯的方式去享受生命，我就感到现实的残酷。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 115,
